name: SVG (basic support)
description: Method of displaying basic Vector Graphics features using the embed or object elements. Refers to the SVG 1.1 spec.

byNum.1: Partial support in Android 3 & 4 refers to not supporting masking.
byNum.2: Partial support in IE9-11 refers to not supporting animations.
byNum.3: IE9-11 & Edge don't properly scale SVG files. [Adding height, width, viewBox, and CSS rules](https://codepen.io/tomByrer/pen/qEBbzw?editors=110) seems to be the best workaround.
